 *      CT3 date and time functions
 *  $ONELINER$
 *      _B_egin _O_f _M_onth
 *  $SYNTAX$
 *      BOM ([<dDate>]) -> dDateBeginOfMonth
 *  $ARGUMENTS$
 *  $RETURNS$
 *  $DESCRIPTION$
 *      TODO: add documentation
